       The pptthhrreeaadd--ccoonnffiigg program is a little helper utility for
       easy configuring and building applications based on the
       pthread emulation API of the GNU Portable Threads (pth)
       library.  It can be used to query the C compiler and
       linker flags which are required to correctly compile and
       link the application against the _p_t_h(3) library.

